Skia is a complete 2D graphic library for drawing Text, Geometries, and Images.

 o 3x3 matricies w/ perspective
 o antialiasing, transparency, filters
 o shaders, xfermodes, maskfilters, patheffects
 o subpixel text

Device backends for Skia currently include:

 o Raster
 o OpenGL
 o PDF
 o XPS
 o Picture (for recording and then playing back into another Canvas)

WWW: https://sites.google.com/site/skiadocs/
